<div class="email-header">
  <h1>You're invited to collaborate!</h1>
</div>

<div class="email-body">
  <p>Hi there,</p>
  <p><strong><%= @inviter_name %></strong> has invited you to collaborate on <%= @invitable.class.name == 'List' ? 'a list' : 'a task' %> in Listopia:</p>
  <div style="background-color: #f7f4ee; border: 1px solid #d9d2c1; border-radius: 4px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h2 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #13243a;"><%= @invitable.title %></h2>
    <% if @invitable.description.present? %>
      <p style="margin: 0; color: #666666;"><%= @invitable.description %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <p>Listopia is a powerful list management tool that lets you:</p>
  <ul style="color: #13243a; line-height: 1.8;">
    <li>Create and organize lists for any purpose</li>
    <li>Collaborate with others in real-time</li>
    <li>Track progress and completion</li>
    <li>Access your lists from anywhere</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To accept this invitation, click the link below:</p>
  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="<%= @invitation_url %>" class="button">Accept Invitation</a>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666666; text-align: center;">
    Or copy and paste this link in your browser: <br>
    <a href="<%= @invitation_url %>" style="color: #8a2c2c; word-break: break-all;"><%= @invitation_url %></a>
  </p>
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666666; margin-bottom: 8px;">This invitation will expire in 7 days.</p>
  <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666666;">Thanks,<br><strong>The Listopia Team</strong></p>
</div>
  </body>
</html>